        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I talk to contractors and small construction business owners all the time, and the story is almost always the same: they're running bids in spreadsheets, tracking jobs on sticky notes, and chasing invoices through text messages. It works — until it doesn't. That's exactly the kind of chaos ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Contractor Foreman",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " was built to eliminate.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you've been looking for a single platform that handles everything from estimates to payment collection without requiring a computer science degree to operate, keep reading. This is what Contractor Foreman is, what it does, and why over 800 reviewers on Capterra give it a 4.5-star rating.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Is Contractor Foreman?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Contractor Foreman is an all-in-one construction management platform designed specifically for general contractors, subcontractors, and small-to-mid-size construction companies. It runs on your phone, tablet, and desktop browser — meaning you can pull up project details from the office trailer or the job site itself.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The core promise is straightforward: replace the patchwork of tools you're currently juggling with a single dashboard. We're talking about budgeting, scheduling, work orders, daily logs, time tracking, document storage, invoicing, and client communication — all under one roof.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://try.contractorforeman.com/ufxanryzfnpw"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What caught my attention first was the price. Plans start at ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "$49 per month",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " with no device limit and unlimited storage. For a tool that covers this much ground, that's genuinely affordable, especially when you consider that some competitors charge that much for project management alone. And there's a ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "100-day money-back guarantee",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", which tells me the team behind it is confident you'll stick around once you try it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
