            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Contractor Foreman is all-in-one construction management software used by general contractors, subcontractors, and small construction companies to manage projects, budgets, estimates, invoices, time tracking, daily logs, and client communication — all from a single dashboard accessible on phone, tablet, or desktop.",
