        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Plans start at $49/month for the Basic tier, which includes unlimited storage, free training and support, a price-lock guarantee, and no device limits. Higher-tier plans (Standard at $105/mo, Advanced at $149/mo, and Complete at $199/mo) add advanced reporting, financial tools, and integrations. A free trial is available.",
